[[File:LocationLiberia.svg|right|180px]] [[File:Flag of Liberia.svg|right|180px]] '''Liberia''' nye [[Afrika]] dukɔwo dometɔawo ɖeka. Ele [[Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe]] lɔƒo. Edo liƒo kple [[Côte d'Ivoire]], [[Guinea]] kpakple [[Sierra Leone]]. Aƒu si woyɔna be [[{{SIL|Atlantic Ocean}}]] la le eƒe ɣetoɖoƒe lɔƒo.
{{Afrika dukɔwo}}
[[Category:Afrika dukɔwo]] [[Category:Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe dukɔwo]]

[[File:LocationNigeria.svg|right|180px]] [[File:Flag of Nigeria.svg|right|180px]] '''Naidzeria''' enye [[Afrika]] dukɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele [[Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe]] lɔƒo. Edo liƒo kple [[Benɛ̃]] le eƒe ɣetoɖoƒe kpadzi, [[Tsyadi]] kple [[Kamerun]] le eƒe ɣedzeƒe lɔƒo, kple [[Nidzɛ]] le eƒe dzigbe. Aƒu si woyɔna be ''[[Gulf of Guinea]]'' la le eƒe anyigbe lɔƒo. Nigeria ƒe dugã enye [[Abuja]]. Gbe si wogblɔna le dɔwɔƒewo enye [[Eŋlisigbe]].
{{Afrika dukɔwo}}
[[Category:Afrika dukɔwo]] [[Category:Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe dukɔwo]]

