Wotsɔ tatia sia tso [[w:en:Template:SeptemberCalendar2007]] me le Eŋlisi Wikipiɖiaa me.<br>
====Legend:====
*Mia bɔwo yia [[Dasiamime 2007]] (ne wonya ŋlɔe daɖi ko);
*Ɣletia ƒe ŋkɔ yia [[Anyɔnyɔ 2007]] (ditto);
*Ɖusi bɔwo yia [[Kele 2007]] (ditto);
*Ŋkekeawo katã ku ɖe ŋkeke si sɔ kple woƒe xexleme ŋu.
*Roma nuŋɔŋlɔwo ku ɖe [[2007|2007 <small>'''(MMVII)'''</small>]] axaa ŋu.

