{{Ŋkekewo le kɔsiɖaa me}}
{{Commonscat|Days of the week}}

[[Category:Ŋkekewo]]
[[Category:Kɔsiɖawo]]

[[File:Les Très Riches Heures du duc de Berry mars.jpg|thumb|right|Mars, tso ''Très riches heures du duc de Berry'']] [[File:YamsatBrixtonMarket.jpg|thumb|right|Tewo le asime]] '''Tedoxe''' (alo '''Mars''') enye [[ɣleti]] etɔ̃lia le [[Gregoria ɣletigbalẽ]]a me. Ŋkeke 31 ye le eme. Le blema ŋɔli la, Romatɔwo yɔna ɣleti sia be ''Martius'' si nye woƒe aʋa mawu ƒe ŋkɔ. Eʋeawo yɔna ɣleti sia be Tedoxe elabena ɣemaɣi sia wodona [[te]] le wode.
== Ŋkeke tɔxewo le Tedoxe me == * [[Ghana]] xɔ ɖokuisinɔnɔ tso [[Eŋlisiawo]] gbɔ. ([[Tedoxe 6]]) * ''Ash Wednesday'' (Kuɖagbea ɖe tso [[Dzodze 4]] vaseɖe [[Tedoxe10]]) * "''The Ides of March''", [[Brutus]] kple ame bubuwo wu [[Yulius Kaesar]] [[Cassius]] ([[Tedoxe 15]]) * [[Norouz]]: Ƒe yeye zã le [[Iran]] kple du bubu aɖewo me. Mɔkeke le [[Turkey]], [[Japan]], kplu Asia titina dukɔwo hã. * [[Fiɖa Kɔkɔe]] (Fiɖaa ɖe tso [[Tedoxe 20]] vaseɖe [[Afɔfiɛ 23]], si nye [[Fiɖa]]mamlea hafi ''[[Easter]]'' ɖuɖu.) * ''[[Easter]]'' (Kɔsiɖaa ɖe tso [[Tedoxe 22]] vaseɖe [[Afɔfiɛ 25]]) * [[Pakistan]] Ŋkeke ([[Tedoxe 23]]). * [[Nyɔnuwo le xexeame godo ƒe ŋkeke]] ([[Tedoxe 8]])
== Nya siawo ƒe tsoƒe == * [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=March&oldid=144167035 Tedoxe le Eŋlisi Wikipiɖia la me] - Dasiamime 13, 2007
{{Commons|March}}
{{Ɣletiawo le ƒea me}}
[[Category:Ɣletiwo]] [[Category:Tedoxe| ]]

[[File:LocationGuinea.svg|right|180px]] [[File:Flag of Guinea.svg|right|180px]] '''Gini''' enye dukɔ si le [[Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe]] kpadzi lɔƒo. Edo liƒo [[Senegal]] le eƒe dzigbe, eye [[Gini Bisao]] le eƒe ɣetoɖoƒe, eye [[Mali]] le eƒe dzigbe vayi eƒe ɣedzeƒe lɔƒo, eye [[Nyiɖu Ƒuta]] le eƒe ɣedzeƒe lɔƒo, eye kple [[Liberia]] kple [[Sira Liɔ̃]] le eƒe anyigbe lɔƒo. Aƒu si woyɔna be [[Atlantika Ƒu]] la le eƒe ɣetoɖoƒe lɔƒo. Gini ƒe dugã enye [[Conakry]]. Gbe si wogblɔna le dɔwɔƒewo le dua me enye [[Fransegbe]].
