'''Adeɛmekpɔxe''' (alo '''November''') enye ɣleti wuiɖekɛlia le ƒea me le [[Gregoria ɣletigbalẽ]]a me. Ŋkeke 30 ye le ɣletia me.
{{Ɣletiawo le ƒea me}}
[[Category:Ɣletiwo]] [[Category:Adeɛmekpɔxe]]

[[File:LocationCapeVerde.svg|right|180px]] [[File:Flag of Cape Verde.svg|right|180px]] '''Cape Verde''' nye dukɔ si le [[Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe]] kpadzi lɔƒo. Medo liƒo kple dukɔa ɖeke o. Aƒu si woyɔna be [[{{SIL|Atlantic Ocean}}]] la ƒoxlãe. Dukɔ si te ɖe dukɔa ŋu wu enye [[Senegal]]. Cape Verde ƒe dugã enye [[Praia]]. Gbe si wogblɔna le woƒe dɔwɔƒewo le dua me enye [[Pɔtugisgbe]].
{{Afrika dukɔwo}}
[[Category:Afrika dukɔwo]] [[Category:Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe dukɔwo]]

'''Pɔlisigbe''' (''język polski'', ''polszczyzna'') nye [[Poland|Polandtɔwo]] ƒe gbegbɔgblɔ̃.
{{stub}}
[[Category:Gbewo]]

'''Pɔtugisgbe''' (''português'', ''língua portuguesa'') nye [[Portugal|Portugaltɔwo]] ƒe gbegbɔgblɔ̃.
{{stub}}
[[Category:Gbewo]]

[[File:LocationGambia.svg|right|180px]] [[File:Flag of The Gambia.svg|right|180px]] [[File:TheGambia Divisions.png|thumb|right|Gambia dukɔa ƒe nɔnɔmetata]] '''Gambia''' nye [[Afrika]] dukɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele [[Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe]] lɔƒo. Gambia do liƒo kple [[Senegal]] le axa etɔ̃ dzi sɔ̃. Aƒu si woyɔna be [[{{SIL|Atlantic Ocean}}]] la le eƒe ɣetoɖoƒe lɔƒo. Eƒe dukɔmenɔlawo ƒe xexlẽme le 1,700,000 lɔƒo.
Gambia dukɔa xɔ dokuisinɔnɔ tso Eŋlisiawo gbɔ le [[Dzodze]] ƒe ŋkeke 18 dzi le ƒe 1965 dzi me. Gambia ƒe dugã enye [[Banjul]]. Gambia ƒe dukplɔla gbãtɔ enye Sir [[Dawda Kairaba Jawara]]. Amesi enye dziɖula fifia enye [[Yahya Jammeh]]. Ele dziɖum tso [[Siamlɔm]] 1994. {{Afrika dukɔwo}}
[[Category:Gambia| ]] [[Category:Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe dukɔwo]]

[[File:LocationGuineaBissau.svg|right|180px]] [[File:Flag of Guinea-Bissau.svg|right|180px]] '''Gini Bisao''' enye dukɔ si le [[Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe]] kpadzi lɔƒo. Edo liƒo [[Senegal]] le eƒe dzigbe, eye [[Gini]] ƒo xlãae tso eƒe ɣedzeƒe lɔƒo vayi eƒe anyigbe. Aƒu si woyɔna be [[Atlantika Ƒu]] la le eƒe ɣetoɖoƒe lɔƒo.
{{Afrika dukɔwo}}
[[Category:Afrika dukɔwo]] [[Category:Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe dukɔwo]]

